channel.description:
This is my first time ever coding a server, sure im a noobie go ahead and make fun of me all you want but i need somone who can help me with a couple errors i'm getting,
First i downloaded TeamTorva (Known as "Torva Pk") - The source runs good then the client won't even open there's a 64 bit a Run normal, and a wind7 all of them won't open not sure why.
Second download was Matrix 666 - I got it to start up but it won't go past the updating/ fetching updates phase any help on that?
The last server i downloaded - It runs very good on source but the client says "Error js5connect", The game play page comes up but it doesn't even load
PLEASE SOMONE WITH BRAINSSS HELP MEEEEEEEEEE Go ahead and flame in the comments you're wasting your own time. Please email me or just leave a comment or even better PM ME :)

item.dc:creator: @pow_err pow err
item.description:
@pow_err wrote:

-SOURCE

@echo off
title Project Insanity
java -Xmx800m -cp bin;deps/poi.jar;deps/mysql.jar;deps/mina.jar;deps/slf4j.jar;deps/slf4j-nop.jar;deps/jython.jar;log4j-1.2.15.jar; server.Server
start Run-Server.bat
exit

[b]

-CLIENT[/b]

Normal run:

@echo off
Title Client
cd ./Class/
START java -Xmx512m Gui 30 0 lowmem members 32
exit

64 bit run:

@echo off
Title Client
cd ./Class/
“C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin\java.exe” -Xmx500m Gui 30 0 lowmem members 32
exit

wind7 run:

@echo off
title Client
cd ./Class/
“C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin\java.exe” -Xmx500m Gui 30 0 lowmem members 32
pause

item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

First off, stick to one source.
Second, Torva Pk probably wasn’t opening because you didn’t have jre/jdk installed, or you don’t have classpaths set up.
Third, Matrix wouldn’t go past updating because the server needs to be on to connect to the client.
Fourth, the js5connect is also a cache to client issue.
